            | &#x9;&#x9;&#x9;&#x9;
            .greenbox.Boxes.wow.slideInLeft.item_left
              span
                img(src='Czar - King Of Wordpress Themes_files/icon-img-3.png')
            | &#x9;&#x9;&#x9;&#x9;
            .Boxes.wow.slideInRight.item_right
              h3 同步服务器
              | &#x9;&#x9;&#x9;&#x9;&#x9;
              p
                | Do you have a lot of requests coming in through website? Don&rsquo;t worry with Zootash and Czar combined, you can create multiple agents to attend to these clients requests.
            | &#x9;&#x9;&#x9;&#x9;
            .Boxes.wow.slideInLeft.item_left
              h3 多用户登陆
              | &#x9;&#x9;&#x9;&#x9;&#x9;
              p
                | Zootash lets to create multiple support departments such as Accounts, Marketing, Support and so on. You can assign tickets to agents based on the support department selected by your customer while filling the form.
            | &#x9;&#x9;&#x9;&#x9;
            .greenbox.Boxes.wow.slideInRight.item_right
              span
                img(src='Czar - King Of Wordpress Themes_files/icon-img-4.png')
            | &#x9;&#x9;&#x9;&#x9;
            .greenbox.Boxes.wow.slideInLeft.item_left
              span
                img(src='Czar - King Of Wordpress Themes_files/icon-img-5.png')
