              h3 404 页面
              | &#x9;&#x9;&#x9;&#x9;&#x9;
              p
                | This plugin lets you create Custom 404 pages for your wordpress website. Use the built in elements, shortcodes and more to create your own customised layouts for 404 page.
            | &#x9;&#x9;&#x9;&#x9;
            .col-md-4.pluginBoxes.wow.bounceInUp.item_fade
              img(src='Czar - King Of Wordpress Themes_files/plugin-icon-2.png')
              | &#x9;&#x9;&#x9;&#x9;&#x9;
              h3 更多的章节
              | &#x9;&#x9;&#x9;&#x9;&#x9;
              p
                | Need a Coming Soon landing page while you create your website? With Czar you don&rsquo;t need to buy any additional plugin to create your coming soon landing pages.
            | &#x9;&#x9;&#x9;&#x9;
            .col-md-4.pluginBoxes.wow.slideInRight.item_fade
              img(src='Czar - King Of Wordpress Themes_files/plugin-icon-3.png')
              | &#x9;&#x9;&#x9;&#x9;&#x9;
              h3 重力系统
              | &#x9;&#x9;&#x9;&#x9;&#x9;
              p
                | With smooth scroll plugin activated you can modify the scroll behavior of the user on the website. This plugin has various options which enhance the experience of the user.
            | &#x9;&#x9;&#x9;&#x9;
            .col-md-4.pluginBoxes.wow.slideInLeft.item_fade
              img(src='Czar - King Of Wordpress Themes_files/plugin-icon-4.png')
              | &#x9;&#x9;&#x9;&#x9;&#x9;
              h3 查询问题解答
              | &#x9;&#x9;&#x9;&#x9;&#x9;
              p
                | Czar is the only wordpress theme which takes care of everything. It has a built in customer support desk called &ldquo;Zootash&rdquo;. No need for you to spend additional monthly recurring costs on expensive support systems.
            | &#x9;&#x9;&#x9;&#x9;
            .col-md-4.pluginBoxes.wow.bounceInUp.item_fade
              img(src='Czar - King Of Wordpress Themes_files/plugin-icon-5.png')
              | &#x9;&#x9;&#x9;&#x9;&#x9;
              h3 管卡完成情况
              | &#x9;&#x9;&#x9;&#x9;&#x9;
              p
                | Member Dash takes the customer support experiece to another level. Using this the customer support agents would not have to login to wordpress dashboard, but can manage the tickets through their account on wordpress frontend itself.
            | &#x9;&#x9;&#x9;&#x9;
            .col-md-4.pluginBoxes.wow.slideInRight.item_fade
              img(src='Czar - King Of Wordpress Themes_files/plugin-icon-6.png')
              | &#x9;&#x9;&#x9;&#x9;&#x9;
              h3 漂亮的布局
              | &#x9;&#x9;&#x9;&#x9;&#x9;
              p
                | Want your users to take that desired action on your website? Sticky Sidebar helps you do just that. You can make various widgets in sidebar sticky and these widgets will remian on user&rsquo;s screen enticing him to take that action.
            | &#x9;&#x9;&#x9;&#x9;
            .col-md-4.pluginBoxes.wow.slideInLeft.item_fade
              img(src='Czar - King Of Wordpress Themes_files/plugin-icon-7.png')
              | &#x9;&#x9;&#x9;&#x9;&#x9;
              h3 客户端下载
              | &#x9;&#x9;&#x9;&#x9;&#x9;
              p
                | With Czar importing demo content into your theme is super easy. All you have to do is click on the content that you want to import and that&rsquo;s it, you are done!!
            | &#x9;&#x9;&#x9;&#x9;
            .col-md-4.pluginBoxes.wow.slideInUp.item_fade
              img(src='Czar - King Of Wordpress Themes_files/plugin-icon-8.png')
              | &#x9;&#x9;&#x9;&#x9;&#x9;
              h3 多屏幕适配
              | &#x9;&#x9;&#x9;&#x9;&#x9;
              p
                | Advance Pop Up for Czar lets you create conditional popups based on user behaviour. This is really impactful and helps you get signups and trigger alerts when user is about to leave the website.
            | &#x9;&#x9;&#x9;&#x9;
            .col-md-4.pluginBoxes.wow.slideInRight.item_fade
              img(src='Czar - King Of Wordpress Themes_files/plugin-icon-9.png')
              | &#x9;&#x9;&#x9;&#x9;&#x9;
              h3 魔法系统（下个版本）
              | &#x9;&#x9;&#x9;&#x9;&#x9;
              p
                | Czar comes with a plugin for automatic updates for the theme. As soon as we release a new update to Czar, the updates are automatically downloaded and applied on your theme. Still prefer manual updates to your theme? No worries,the plugin can be configured to do just that.
          | &#x9;&#x9;&#x9;
